data.description: ****Price Improvement***  Seller is offering $1,500.00 towards closing cost. Ready To Move in Townhome in an amazing location with a well established neighborhood. Calling all investors and first time home buyers. Two-story townhome withing minutes of I-85 and I-40. Open kitchen with new flooring, carpet, and quartz countertop. 3br, 2.5 bath including walk in closet with washer and dryer included. 15 minutes from downtown Durham, DPAC, Durham bulls stadium and less than 5 minutes from the new Northern High School.
